<div class="container">

  <div class="row header">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h2>An Exceptional College Core Program</h2>
      <p>Don't just take the college core curriculum.  <strong>Experience</strong> it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row feature">
    <div class="col-md-6 info">
      <h4>Study one subject at a time...</h4>
      <p>
        Each subject deserves your full attention.  Our sequenced, modular curriculum will enable you to discover the
        rich, profound significance God placed in the liberal arts.
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 image" %>
      <%= image_tag 'focus-01.png', class:'img-responsive' %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= content_tag :div, nil, class:'divider' %>

  <div class="row feature backwards">
    <div class="col-md-6 info">
      <h4>...in the flow of the biblical narrative.</h4>
      <p>
        Cultivate a love for learning by discovering the unity of knowledge.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 image" %>
      <%= image_tag 'biblical_narrative.png', class:'img-responsive' %>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>